    "**Accurate data is the foundation of any good business decision.** \n",
    "OpenAI’s latest models like o3, o4-mini, and the GPT-4.1 family are enabling businesses to build state-of-the-art retrieval systems for their most important workflows. However, information evolves rapidly: facts ingested confidently yesterday may already be outdated today.\n",
